      "message": "This breaks builds unfortunately. An example [1].\n\nThe `jenkins/gerrit-bazel-get-project-info.sh` now uses `{project-infor-output}`, which defaults to `{repo}`.\nHowever Jenkins Job Builder expands {project-info-output} once, but it does not expand the resulting {name} again, so we are getting:\n\n```\n13:43:13 [plugin-metrics-reporter-graphite-bazel-stable-3.12] $ /bin/bash -e /tmp/jenkins16517889394170025624.sh\n13:43:13 /tmp/jenkins16517889394170025624.sh: line 4: bazel-bin/plugins/{name}/{name}.json: No such file or directory\n```\n\n[1] https://gerrit-ci.gerritforge.com/view/Plugins-stable-3.12/job/plugin-metrics-reporter-graphite-bazel-stable-3.12/1/console",
